#. REF: sc21
msgctxt "mn134:14.17"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā. "
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said. "

msgctxt "mn134:14.18"
msgid "Attamano āyasmā lomasakaṅgiyo bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandīti. "
msgstr "Satisfied, Venerable Lomasakaṅgiya was happy with what the Buddha said. "

